 					Cloud - Advantages		

1. cost reduction in  IT operations

2. Accessibility from anywhere

	australia - india - cloud - online - resources -
3. Availability of Resources on demands - 24 * 7 * 365

4. ** Up front Investment not required 

Use case :   	Start up companies - boom
 			lease - resources - use it  - pay per use - after the use....

Use case :		Netflix - World movie website - own servers - cloud 100%

5. Maintenance headache are gone 

	traditional - buy servers - setup - maintain
		
	cloud - vendor - demand of resources - enjoy services - ** cost reduction

6. 	Cloud vendors - they will take care of end to end activities like - 

 Updates
 Disaster mgmt
 Support
 License cost 
Data Mgmt etc

7. Cloud vendors offer a lot of services

8. It is a boom for the companies to focus on their core competency.

Ex- pharma companies


Cloud - Concerns

1. the internet is  a dependency, some parts of the world still do not have internet access.

	Example: South African countries, cloud still a question

2. broadband internet - slowness - 

3. Vendor - 24 * 7 -- > service issues - * down time - concern for ur business

	Unplanned - concern

4. *** vendor lock in issue ***

--> 2020 - azure - setup -- using -- not satisfied --> 2021 - aws --> down times ** 3 days **

	- sneap deal - azure --> 2021 - aws -- down time - 3 days

	7 --5 -3 --> 1 to 3 days...;; Live migration (chargeable)

5. Cloud - 100 % not flexible or not custom
tradition --> custom - will --> 100 %
	
	cloud --> 100 % --> 95 % is possible

